Meta-Analysis (Dictator Game)

Liam A. Doyle

2024-07-05

Project Description

This is an R Markdown file that documents for some of the analyses conducted for the first study in my dissertation. Specifically, this file documents the multi-level meta-analytic model conducted for the effect of psychopathy on behaviour in the Dictator Game.
